OL,3,CBroadcaster John Stapleton has died
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,FBroadcaster John Stapleton died in
OL,7,Fhospital on Sunday morning at the age
OL,8,Fof 79, his agent has said.
OL,10,FJackie Gill said: "John had
OL,11,FParkinson's disease which was
OL,12,Fcomplicated by pneumonia. His son Nick
OL,13,Fand daughter-in-law Lisa have been
OL,14,Fconstantly at his side and John died
OL,15,Fpeacefully in hospital this morning."
OL,17,FStapleton was a fixture of broadcast
OL,18,Fnews and presented on programmes
OL,19,Fincluding TV-am, Daybreak, GMTV,
OL,20,FNewsnight and Panorama.
