OL,3,CBroadcaster John Stapleton has died
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,FHe held a distinguished career
OL,7,Fspanning over 50 years, becoming one
OL,8,Fof the most recognisable figures in UK
OL,9,Ftelevision news.
OL,11,FStapleton began his career in
OL,12,Fjournalism in the 1960s, working for
OL,13,Flocal newspapers before moving into
OL,14,Fbroadcasting with the BBC in the 1970s.
OL,16,FHe became a reporter for the flagship
OL,17,Fcurrent affairs programme Newsnight
OL,18,Fwhen it launched in 1980.
