OL,3,CBroadcaster John Stapleton has died
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,FIn 1983, he joined the launch team of
OL,7,FTV-am. He moved to BBC's Watchdog in
OL,8,Fthe late 1980s, where he co-presented
OL,9,Fthe consumer affairs programme
OL,10,Falongside his wife, the late Lynn
OL,11,FFaulds Wood.
OL,13,FIn 1993, Stapleton joined GMTV, where
OL,14,Fhe remained a key figure for over a
OL,15,Fdecade.
OL,17,FFollowing GMTV's closure in 2010,
OL,18,FStapleton continued his career with
OL,19,FITV's Daybreak and later Good Morning
OL,20,FBritain (GMB), where he appeared
OL,21,Fregularly until 2015.
