OL,3,CBroadcaster John Stapleton has died
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,FThe veteran journalist shared his
OL,7,FParkinson's diagnosis in October 2024.
OL,9,FAppearing on ITV's Good Morning
OL,10,FBritain after announcing his
OL,11,Fdiagnosis, he said: "There's no point
OL,12,Fin being miserable... It won't ever
OL,13,Fchange.
OL,15,F"I mean, Parkinson's is here with me
OL,16,Fnow for the rest of my life. Best I
OL,17,Fcan do is try and control it and take
OL,18,Fthe advice of all the experts."
